<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`In the last chapter, we saw some main ideas about Redux. Now, we want to create an app. We will have async (like AJAX) calls in this.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`We're going to create a webpage that will search for cities and give back Temp, Pressure and Humidity.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`We will use things like a line chart for the temp etc.`}</MDXTag>
